  (eforall (eforall (econst "True" lnil) ([x] (esort (lvar liz)))) ([x] (eforall (eapp x (econst "True.intro" lnil)) ([y] (eforall (econst "True" lnil) ([z] (eapp x z)))))))
  (esort True_rec/type-wf-sort)
   = (defeq/forall
       (defeq/forall
         (defeq/const True/decl (inst-expr/sort lvl-inst/zero))
         ([x] ([h] defeq/sort-refl)))
       ([x]
         ([h]
           (defeq/forall
             (defeq/app
               h
               (defeq/const True_intro/decl (inst-expr/const lvls-inst/nil)))
             ([y]
               ([h1]
                 (defeq/forall
                   (defeq/const True/decl (inst-expr/sort lvl-inst/zero))
                   ([z] ([h2] (defeq/app h h2)))))))))).

